title: Onslow - Quartet & Quintet - Carracilly (1987)
description:
Composer: George Onslow

Work: Quartet op. 8/1, Quintet Op. 78.

Played by: Carracilly, Tournus, Pasquier, Jarry, Collot 

Record label and date: Charlin, 1987


1. Quintet for strings No. 32 in D minor, Op. 78: Allegro Patetico
2. Quintet for strings No. 32 in D minor, Op. 78: Scherzo: Impetuoso
3. Quintet for strings No. 32 in D minor, Op. 78: Romanza: Andantino Affectuoso
4. Quintet for strings No. 32 in D minor, Op. 78: Finale: Agitato Molto Vivace
5. Quartet No. 1, Op. 8/1: Allegro
6. Quartet No. 1, Op. 8/1: Adagio
7. Quartet No. 1, Op. 8/1: Minuetto: Allegro e Risoluto
8. Quartet No. 1, Op. 8/1: Finale: Presto
